        <abstract>
            <t>Different traffic engineering approaches as well as operational tools in ISIS could benefit
                from understanding at what precise time a specific fragment has been generated and flooded out by a node.
                This document introduces an optional TLV that can be carried on fragments to encode such information.
            </t>


        </abstract>

